-- Rio Tinto Wins Heavy Sands License in Mozambique, Noticias Says
-- B y   F r e d   K a t e r e r e
-- 2010-11-22T04:30:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-22/rio-tinto-wins-heavy-sands-license-in-mozambique-noticias-says.html
Rio Tinto Group has been awarded a
license to mine for heavy sands in a concession in southern Gaza
and Inhambane provinces, the state-run Noticias reported, citing
Mineral Resources Minister Esperanca Bias.   To contact the reporter on this story:
